message: Focus on cooking individual proteins and vegetables with the stove first. Combining a cooked protein with one cooked vegetable usually results in value 60. Combining a cooked protein with two cooked vegetables often results in value 80. Be very cautious with grains; combining cooked grains with a high-value dish (like 80) can drastically reduce its value.
